room_title: Escape room "Sector 8 - Area 51" by Escape Room Clearwater Beach in Tampa
room_description: Under mounting scrutiny about the activities conducted at the Groom Lake Research Facility (a.k.a Area 51), the U.S. Government relocated its most sensitive research projects to various secret facilities around the nation. Sector 8, a top-secret research laboratory was among these projects and was relocated to Clearwater Beach, Florida in the mid-90's. It was thought that the research was complete and the project was dormant, but in the last few days the test subjects have revolted and taken over the facility.
